The paper deals with computational complexity and approximation algorithms for two problems related to strings and sequences. The topics covered in the paper are closely related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), computational geometry (cs.CG), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), and game theory (cs.GT). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
